text: Arrifana () is a Portuguese parish, located in the municipality of Santa Maria da Feira. The population in 2011 was 6,551,Instituto Nacional de Estatística in an area of 5.29 km².Eurostat Its local inhabitants are known as Arrifanense. ==Sporting clubs== *Clube Desportivo Arrifanense ==References== Category:Parishes of Santa Maria da Feira
